NoGolems v1.0 by mstiles92

This simple Bukkit plugin allows you to control who is able to build snow golems and iron golems.

Permissions:
nogolems.allow.all: Allow building of all golems.
nogolems.allow.snow: Allow snow golems to be built. 
nogolems.allow.iron: Allow iron golems to be built.

Originally requested at http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/block-players-from-creating-golems-formatted.88808/
Hosted on BukkitDev at http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/nogolems/